      </p>
      <p>Brad has a passion for data models, prototyping, leveraging APIs and solving problems through web applications.</p>

      <p>Brad has 5 years of experience as a consulting sales engineer with the SQL Server BI technologies, quantifying technical
        requirements and over 20 years experience as a small business owner delivering technical services directly to businesses
        and consumers.</p>
      <p>
