        business to over 2000 customers in the Boston area. His love of technology, 3D modelling software, contact management
        applications and online appointment scheduling inspired his interest in pursuing a technology career.
      </p>
      <p>Brad has a strong work ethic, a passion for constantly learning new technologies and a heart for teaching.</p>
